-- Microsoft names head for online services group
-- 
-- Thu Dec 4, 2008 5:37pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/12/04/us-brief-microsoft-idUSTRE4B37W020081204

 

 (Reuters) - Microsoft Corp ( MSFT.O ) has appoints Dr. Qi Lu to run online its services group. 

 * Says Lu most recently served as executive vice president of Engineering for the search and advertising technology group at Yahoo.